data.description: VA Loan assumption possible and special financing options as well. A luxury traditional home nestled in the highly sought after Oakland Springs community. This home is equipped with granite countertops, gas stove and fireplace, premium wood flooring, tile and carpet through out, low maintenance yard and a cozy patio. This home is located in a great location; near schools, stores, parks, amenities, 20 minute drive to Toyota stadium, Red Stone Arsenal, golf courses and the best of what Madison and Huntsville have to offer. Currently zoned for Madison City Schools. If you are looking for the perfect home in a pristine community. then look no further! Schedule your showing today!
